  "title": "How efficient are futures market operations in mitigating price risk? an explorative analysis",
  "abstract": "This paper investigates the efficiency of futures markets in prices of important cereals. Findings show that the variation in the spot and futures prices is high in the case of urad, wheat and jeera.",
